<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><html xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="http://www.langmaster.com/new/author/coursemodelschema.xsd">
  <head>
    <title>Speaking part</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <extension data="chinh-speaking">
      <![CDATA[
data      
    ]]>
    </extension>
    <div id="chinh-speaking-dialog" class="modal fade">
      <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-body">
            <div id="instruction1">
              <div class="alert alert-warning">
                <p>
                  Poslechnete si otazku. Po jejim prehrani zazni gong. Po zazneni gongu zacnete ihned nahravat Vasi odpoved do mikrofonu.
                </p>
                <div class="btn btn-warning" data-bind="click: Course.extension.instructionOK">OK, rozumim.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div id="instruction2">
              <div class="alert alert-warning">
                <p>
                  Prectete si otazku. Po jedne minute na rozmysleni zazni gong. Po zazneni gongu zacnete ihned nahravat Vasi odpoved do mikrofonu.
                </p>
                <div class="btn btn-warning" data-bind="click: Course.extension.instructionOK">OK, rozumim.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div id="playing-question" class="info">
              <h3>playing question...</h3>
            </div>
            <div id="recording" class="info">
              <h3>recording...</h3>
            </div>
            <div id="saving-recording" class="info">
              <h3>saving your recording...</h3>
            </div>
            <div id="thinking" class="info">
              <h3>
                one minute for thinking (<span data-bind="text:Course.extension.remaining"></span> seconds remaining)...
              </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="show">
              <media-big-mark media-url="/lm/examples/moe_test/Speaking/Speaking/media/gong.mp3" id="gong"></media-big-mark>
            </div>
            <div id="part1-question1">
              <media-big-mark media-url="/lm/examples/moe_test/Speaking/Speaking/media/part1_question1.mp3" id="p1-q1"></media-big-mark>
              <recording id="p1-a1" limit-max="6"></recording>
            </div>
            <div id="part1-question2">
              <media-big-mark media-url="/lm/examples/moe_test/Speaking/Speaking/media/part1_question2.mp3" id="p1-q2"></media-big-mark>
              <recording id="p1-a2" limit-max="6"></recording>
            </div>
            <div id="part1-question3">
              <media-big-mark media-url="/lm/examples/moe_test/Speaking/Speaking/media/part1_question3.mp3" id="p1-q3"></media-big-mark>
              <recording id="p1-a3" limit-max="6"></recording>
            </div>
            <hr />
            <div id="part2-question">
              <div id="p2-q1">
                <div class="panel panel-info" id="part2">
                  <div class="panel-heading">
                    <p>Read a situation with three possible solutions below. Choose which of the three solutions is the best and discuss why it is the better than the others. You have 1 minute to prepare and a maximum of 2 minutes to respond. </p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>You got on the bus to school. A moment later, the bus attendant asks for your bus pass. In that moment, you realized that you had forgotten your bus pass and you don’t have any cash with you. What would you do?</p>
                    <ul>
                      <li>
                        ask money from a stranger
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        get off the bus, go home, and be late for school
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        ask the bus driver politely if you can pay tomorrow
                      </li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <recording id="p2-a1" limit-max="12" />
            </div>
            <hr />
            <div id="part3-question1">
              <div id="p3-q1">
                <div class="panel panel-info" id="part3">
                  <div class="panel-heading">
                    <p>Make a response to the topic below and develop your ideas using the clues provided. Then answer some questions related to the topic.</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>Describe a possession you couldn’t live without. You should say: </p>
                    <ul>
                      <li>
                        what you use it for
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        why it is important to you
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        where you got it from
                      </li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <recording id="p3-a1" limit-max="120"></recording>
            </div>
            <hr />
            <div id="part3-question2">
              <media-big-mark media-url="/lm/examples/moe_test/Speaking/Speaking/media/part3_question2.mp3" id="p3-q2"></media-big-mark>
              <recording id="p3-a2" limit-max="60"></recording>
            </div>
            <div id="part3-question3">
              <media-big-mark media-url="/lm/examples/moe_test/Speaking/Speaking/media/part3_question3.mp3" id="p3-q3"></media-big-mark>
              <recording id="p3-a3" limit-max="60"></recording>
            </div>
            <div id="part3-question4">
              <media-big-mark media-url="/lm/examples/moe_test/Speaking/Speaking/media/part3_question4.mp3" id="p3-q4"></media-big-mark>
              <recording id="p3-a4" limit-max="60"></recording>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-footer">
            <div id="progress-panel" class="show">
              <span class="label" data-bind="css: {'label-default': Course.extension.actIdx()&lt;0, 'label-success': Course.extension.actIdx()&gt;0, 'label-warning': Course.extension.actIdx()==0}">1</span>
              <span class="label" data-bind="css: {'label-default': Course.extension.actIdx()&lt;1, 'label-success': Course.extension.actIdx()&gt;1, 'label-warning': Course.extension.actIdx()==1}">2</span>
              <span class="label" data-bind="css: {'label-default': Course.extension.actIdx()&lt;2, 'label-success': Course.extension.actIdx()&gt;2, 'label-warning': Course.extension.actIdx()==2}">3</span>
              <span class="label" data-bind="css: {'label-default': Course.extension.actIdx()&lt;3, 'label-success': Course.extension.actIdx()&gt;3, 'label-warning': Course.extension.actIdx()==3}">4</span>
              <span class="label" data-bind="css: {'label-default': Course.extension.actIdx()&lt;4, 'label-success': Course.extension.actIdx()&gt;4, 'label-warning': Course.extension.actIdx()==4}">5</span>
              <span class="label" data-bind="css: {'label-default': Course.extension.actIdx()&lt;5, 'label-success': Course.extension.actIdx()&gt;5, 'label-warning': Course.extension.actIdx()==5}">6</span>
              <span class="label" data-bind="css: {'label-default': Course.extension.actIdx()&lt;6, 'label-success': Course.extension.actIdx()&gt;6, 'label-warning': Course.extension.actIdx()==6}">7</span>
              <span class="label" data-bind="css: {'label-default': Course.extension.actIdx()&lt;7, 'label-success': Course.extension.actIdx()&gt;7, 'label-warning': Course.extension.actIdx()==7}">8</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>